    "installation": "Import via Google Fonts in index.html or CSS: @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@500;600;700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono&display=swap');"
